{"tid":2456346,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：加拿大前外交官康明凱案預料今日在北京開審","createTime":"2021-03-22T00:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T00:35:27.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e8ecabf09917a7b47e32b78f609d40fdb9d462d7","tid":2456346,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T00:35:27.000Z","msg":"<strong>加拿大前外交官康明凱涉嫌危害中國國家安全犯罪</strong>的案件，預料今日在北京審訊，康明凱的妻子接受路透社訪問時表示，康明凱及另一名被指涉案的商人邁克爾，都是無辜地捲入地緣政治糾紛<strong>，強調扣押行為極不公正，必須確保他們重獲自由</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n康明凱和邁克爾涉嫌危害中國國家安全，由2018年12月起被扣押至今。中方一直否認事件與華為副董事長孟晚舟被加拿大當局扣押事件有關。<br />\n<br />\n邁克爾上星期五在遼寧省丹東市中級人民法院閉門審訊，法院將依法擇期宣判。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581791-20210322.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581791-20210322.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbRnwB9%2FpnwrfV4lJUXhph6I%3D&h=068aaedf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581791-20210322.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=45ac2ab5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581791-20210322.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}